OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day. There will be
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud throughout
OL,7,Fthe day along with some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Light south or
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,13,Fwith clear periods and the chance of
OL,14,Fsome misty low cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry day with some sunshine
OL,17,Falthough with the chance of some
OL,18,Fpatchy low cloud. Quite warm across
OL,19,FOrkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
